uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.collection

Interface LongStreamDecorator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BaseStream<Long,LongStream>, BaseStreamDecorator<Long,LongStream>, LongStream
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceStream.LongResourceStream

    public interface LongStreamDecorator
extends BaseStreamDecorator<Long,LongStream>, LongStream
    A decorator for a LongStream which wraps intermediate and terminal operations such that they can be easily extended.
